<seg id=1> NASA Has Lost Contact with the Mars Probe, the Spirit </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> (Agence France-Presse, Washington, 22nd) - The officials of United States National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) said today NASA has lost contact with the landed "Spirit" because of a serious breakdown in the rover vehicle. </seg>
