<p>
<seg id=1> Asia is the largest continent on earth, with nearly 30 percent of the world land area and about 60 percent of the world population at this moment. Its economic activities accounted for one quarter of the world's total.  It should and it could make remarkable contribution to world peace and development. </seg>
</p>
