<seg id=8> U.S. took the lead to sanction China and announced the sale of 150 F-16 fighters to Taiwan.  U.S. linked the human right issue with the Most Favored Nation status and allowed Lee Teng-hui to visit America.  The Sino-U.S. relation sank to a low point. </seg>
