<seg id=7> Furthermore, we are appealing for the set up of more comprehensive information disclosure laws such that related institutions or individuals may report suspicious transactions. </seg>
<seg id=8> "Balance" is the key for any work in this area -- it is necessary to have sufficient power for effective investigation and at same time, there has to be appropriate constitutional protection for freedom, individual privacy, efficiency in our economic and financial systems.  These are all factors that have to be considered. </seg>
