<seg id=3> After a recovery in Hong Kong's economy, I also hope Hong Kong can make better use of its own advantage and make greater contribution to the development of our country. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> When I met with Premier Wen Jiabao, I have congratulated him on behalf of Hong Kong for his work in a very difficult year.  Under his leadership, our country has achieved admirable results.  Even though there are still many challenges in the future, you have heard his work report.  He is full of confidence and for that, we are truly inspired. </seg>
