<seg id=7> Later on, I will meet with Mr. Zhang Dejiang, secretary of Guangdong province, and Mr. Huang Huahua, Governor of Guangdong province, and explore with them how to elevate our cooperation to a new level on top of the existing foundation and create a bigger win-win situation. </seg>
</p>
