<seg id=2> We have fought the sudden outbreak of severe acute respiratory syndrome with extreme hardships and difficulties but we finally achieved a great victory at that stage.  The economy in our country continued to maintain a nice growth trend.  We have climbed another step as the average per capita production surged above 1,000 U.S. dollars.  The "Shenzhou 5" manned space flight was concluded with great success and the Chinese people's dream on space flights has been realized.  Our nationals are untied, the society is progressing and people's livings are better than before. </seg>
