<seg id=7> For this, a spokesman of China's Ministry of Foreign Affairs said the objective of the six-party talks is to maintain dialogue and push ahead the peace process.  China is willing to work jointly with other parties on this objective. </seg>
<seg id=8> China's starting point is to maintain peace and stability in the Korean Peninsula and realize denuclearization in the Peninsula. </seg>
