<seg id=4> The textbook is excellent in both pictures and literary compositions.  It employs the story-telling approach to make lively and systematic introductions about the Olympic games and the essence of its spirit.  It is a good educational material to strengthen young students' knowledge about the Olympic games and also help raise the enthusiasm of our society to take part in the Olympic games. </seg>
