<DOC docid="UN20040101.005" sysid="cha">
<p>
<seg id=1> China admires the Counter-Terrorism Committee's efforts to carry out the United Nations 1373(2001) resolution and its contribution to strengthen the anti-terrorism capability in developing countries.  China supports the strengthening of coordination and cooperation between Counter-Terrorism Committee (the "Committee") and related international, regional and sub-regional organizations in its fight against international terrorism. </seg>
<seg id=2> At the same time, we hope the Counter-Terrorism Committee can strive to satisfy the actual demand of developing countries and improve the level of aid in its course of work against terrorism. </seg>
