<seg id=6> Meanwhile, China Weaponry Industry Corp. aggressively pushed forward a structural adjustment including a total of 21 bankruptcies and closure of enterprises.  The total number of staff has decreased from 476 thousand at the time of its formation to 360 thousand now, a decrease of 116 thousand.  Six enterprises have been listed on the stock exchange after restructure. </seg>
