<seg id=9> Perhaps, some people think that the results of the talks are not enough and the process is not fast enough. </seg>
<seg id=10> In my opinion, this round of talks was launched under the circumstances that the parties concerned lacked mutual trust and their differences were enlarged. </seg>
</p>
