<seg id=6> Meanwhile, China Arms Industry Corporation has been making great efforts in the company's restructure, shutting down a total of 21 firms, with the number of employees reduced to 360,000 from 476,000 when the corporation was founded. It has cut off 116,000 employees and has listed 6 reshuffled firms on the stock market. </seg>
