<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency report of January 26 from Tokyo (by staff reporter Le Shaoyan) - Statistics issued by the Japanese Finance Ministry on 26th showed that Japanese import and export trade volume both hit a historical new high in 2003, with trade surplus once again surpassing 10 trillion Japanese Yen after three years. </seg>
