</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> In import, due to the rising demand for energy resources such as oil and natural gas and their soaring prices, Japan's total import volume in 2003 went up 5% from the previous year to reach 44.3202 trillion Japanese Yen, also a record high. </seg>
</p>
<p>
