<seg id=5> Private enterprises outnumbered state-owned or controlled enterprises for the first time. </seg>
<seg id=6> Although the number of State-owned or controlled enterprises decreased during their structural reshuffle, their strength was boosted, with the average registered capital of each enterprise reaching 3.76 million Yuan, up 20% compared with that at the end of 2002. </seg>
