<seg id=8> Abraham said "Rokkasho of Japan's Aomori is the right place for receiving large quantities of materials needed for the set-up of ITER. Your celebrated technology and engineering skills are admired all over the world. Besides, the communities in the locality explicitly welcome this program and wish Rokkasho of Aomori to be selected as its location. " </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> The spokesman of US Embassy in Tokyo confirms that this is the first time for Washington authorities to openly support Japan who is trying to have ITER located in Japan. </seg>
