<seg id=2> This is a slander of the peace efforts by the mainland and a provocation to the relations across the Strait. </seg>
<seg id=3> At present the actual threat to Taiwan security does not come from mainland but from the "Taiwan independence" spitting activities launched on a large scale by the Taiwan authorities. </seg>
<seg id=4> It is the splittism forces of "Taiwan independence" that sabotage the status quo of the relations across the Strait and are the immediate sources of menace against peace in Taiwan. </seg>
