<seg id=7> Since its inception, Consumer Council has received more and more callers from the several thousand annually in 1970s to 146,000 last year, more than 20 times increase. This shows that more and more consumers choose to consult the reports and suggestions of Consumer Council before they make decisions in choosing products and service. </seg>
<seg id=8> Besides, the number of complaints which have been handled by Consumer Council this year exceeds 26,000. </seg>
