<p>
<seg id=1> Since the birth of intellectual property system several hundred years ago, especially since the industrial revolution, important epoch-making inventions have come into being one after another. </seg>
<seg id=2> In the past 20 years the intellectual property system has been an important legal system and a significant policy means in promoting technological innovations and has played a pivotal role in enlivening economy and enhancing international competitive power. </seg>
<seg id=3> At present with  the development of scince and technology and economic globalization by leaps and bounds, creation, possession and utilization of knowledge and intellectual resources, quantities and quality of the possessed intellectual property have become important basis for a country to participate in international competition. </seg>
<seg id=4> Therefore, to intensify the international exchange and cooperation in the protection of intellectual property is of great significance for establishing a just and reasonable new international economic order and for promoting the prosperity and growth of world economy. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> The Chinese government attaches great importance to the protection of intellectual property. </seg>
<seg id=6> In the early days of reform and opening-up, our country began to set up an intellectual property system. Over 20 years of endeavor it has already formed a relatively complete legal system of intellectual property and has forged a protection system of such rights which combines judiciary means with administrative execution of laws. Lots of work has been done in this regard and we have made important contribution to the progress of science and technology and the development of society and economy. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> In the 21st century humankind enters a society of information. The technological revolution will propel the development of social productive forces with tremendous driving force. </seg>
<seg id=8> To further improve the intellectual property system of our country and intensify international exchange and cooperation in the protection of intellectual property are the requirements of the further opening-up to the outside world of our country in the new century, and are also the necessity for building a modern socialist country and achieving the great renewal of the Chinese nation. </seg>
<seg id=9> We are willing to work together with other countries in the world in order to establish a just and reasonable intellectual property system conducive to promoting the development of technology and economy in all countries and to create a good environment in which the whole humankind respects knowledge, advocates science and protects intellectual property. </seg>
</p>
