<seg id=6> Thirdly, US imposes the values of its own country on others as the highest principles and insists on democratic transformation of the Middle East countries. This has met with opposition and some of its allies demand US to respect the culture and characteristics of the Islamic countries. They think that the reason why US troops are caught in the quagmire of Iraq lies in its "failure to respect" it. </seg>
