<p>
<seg id=1> The 3-party talk on Iraqi issue was held at the New York UN headquarters on 19. The UN Secretary General Annan, Provisional Governing Council of Iraq and the Interim Authority of the British and US coalition forces had a discussion mainly on how UN plays its role in the reconstruction of Iraq. </seg>
<seg id=2> The discussion involves the politics, humanity and security of Iraq and the special envoy to be sent to Iraq by UN. The 3 parties had a frank exchange of views. </seg>
