<seg id=7> In fact, for years Qaddafi of unique personality has been opposed to US on the one hand and kept stretching the olive branch to US which however received no response on the other hand. </seg>
<seg id=8> After the Iraqi War was over, the countries in the Middle East readjusted their strategies and the regional forces regrouped themselves. This provides a good opportunity for US and Libya to renew the diplomatic relation. </seg>
