<p>
<seg id=1> US which leads the world in medium field has a lot to say in international press. Its tentacles of public opinion propaganda radiate to all over the world and there is no place they cannot reach. Then why does it spend so much money on a special satellite TV station covering 22 countries in the Middle East? </seg>
