<seg id=3> But some analyst point out that "First Freedom TV" will be America's strategic weapon to carry out cultural infiltration, cultural intrusion and psychological offence in Arab countries. It will be an important propaganda tool for US to reshape the Middle East and transform the Islamic world. </seg>
