<seg id=5> US believes that the Islamic civilization is a serious obstacle to the western efforts in promoting modern civilization. The extreme religious forces in the Middle East Islamic countries are hotbed of international terrorism characteristic of opposing the USA. To effectively fight against terror, the Islamic world must be transformed so that it identifies with and accepts the western values, the western life style and the political system. </seg>
<seg id=6> The US attempts to instill its ideology into Arabs through the imperceptible influence of "First Freedom TV" programs. </seg>
<seg id=7> Secondly, it aims to improve the image of the USA. </seg>
<seg id=8> US abides by unilateralism in its foreign policy. On many international issues it parades its strength and do things at its own will. Its hegemonic acts enrage the Arab countries and the Islamic world. </seg>
