<p>
<seg id=1> A year ago the 9th informal meeting of leaders of Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Organization was held at the riverside of Huangpujiang River in Shanghai. The scene of the meeting is still vivid in my mind. </seg>
<seg id=2> Today we are gathering in the beautiful Los Cabos on the Pacific coast to discuss about the important issues of Asia-Pacific economic cooperation. </seg>
<seg id=3> I am so happy to meet old friends. </seg>
<seg id=4> Here I would like to avail myself of this opportunity to extend my heart-felt thanks to President Fox for his invitation and to the Mexican government for its considerate arrangements. </seg>
