<p>
<seg id=5> In the past year economic globalization kept progressing and science and technology developed with each passing day, which have brought about new development opportunities for all countries. </seg>
<seg id=6> In the meanwhile the uncertainties in the global economic development increased. Some countries and regions including members of Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Organization faced new challenges in the process of their economic development. </seg>
<seg id=7> Trade protectionism is again showing up and we still have a long way to go to effect free, fair and just trade. </seg>
<seg id=8> The anti-terror struggle is arduous and complicated and the non-traditional security factors have increased. </seg>
<seg id=9> This world of ours is still very unstable. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> Although the international community still faces problems of one kind or another and there will be all kinds of unexpected problems ahead, the trend of the day for peace and development cannot be reversed and the wish of the peoples of all countries for a better life has not changed. </seg>
