<DOC docid="XIN20030601.001" sysid="che">
<p>
<seg id=1> This dialogue meeting has the theme of development, which is of great significance. </seg>
<seg id=2> Development is the basis of the progress of human civilization and the key to the settlement of all kinds of contradictions and problems confronting the whole world. </seg>
<seg id=3> Only by realizing global harmony, balance and universal development can the world lasting peace and stability be achieved. </seg>
<seg id=4> We should carry out an all-round and profound discussion of this theme and work as one to settle this problem. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> The fast development of the trend of economic globalization is the most distinguished feature of today's world economy. </seg>
<seg id=6> Propelled by the economic globalization trend, the link between countries and regions is becoming closer day by day; markets are more open; the financial, technological and talent flow is more extensive and faster. All this has brought about an unprecedented opportunity for promoting international cooperation and joint development. </seg>
<seg id=7> At the same time the development of economic globalization has brought about severe challenges. The south-north gap is widening; some developing countries face the danger of further peripheralization; economic and financial risks increase; transnational crimes become serious. All this makes it more necessary and urgent to have international cooperation to deal with such challenges. </seg>
<seg id=8> At this moment when opportunities and challenges coexist, we should seize the chance to deal with challenges, seek common ground and leave aside differences, expand cooperation and promote the development of economic globalization towards joint development and prosperity. </seg>
</p>
</DOC>
