</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency in Lisbon on January 7th (Reporter Zhao Xiaozhong) According to the report of Portuguese media on 7th, the second most elderly female on Guinness World Records Catarina Carreiro, Portugues will celebrate her 113th birthday on 9th together with her family. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Carreiro was born on January 9th, 1891 and now resides in Penha Garcia Town of Castelo Branco of central Portugal. </seg>
<seg id=4> There are 4 generations in her family, 7 children, 26 grandchildren, 39 great grandchildren and 7 great great grandchildren. </seg>
<seg id=5> On her 113th birthday, the 5 generations will get together at her birthday party to congratulate on her birthday. </seg>
<seg id=6> But her family members say that they won't have ostentatious celebrations, for she is weak and gets up in the afternoon every day. </seg>
</p>
