<seg id=7> According to Portuguese media, No.1 most elderly female on Guinness Record is an American named Charlotte Benkner born on November 6th, 1889. </seg>
<seg id=8> Charlotte Benkner and Catarina Carreiro have not yet broken the longevity record set by a French named Jeanne Calment who died in 1997 at the age of 122. </seg>
