<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency in Hong Kong on January 12th (Reporter Liu Shiping) Leung Oi Sie, the secretary for justice of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region said on 12th that Mainland/Hong Kong Closer Economic Partnership Arrangement (CEPA) has won a win-win situation for legal circles on both sides: Hong Kong lawyers benefit from the sustained economic development on the mainland while helping the mainland to improve its professional know-how on international trade and finance. </seg>
