<p>
<seg id=3> Leung Oi Sie said in her address for the opening of the 2004 legal year that the Department of Justice has helped to work out provisions for legal service to CEPA and will continue to make contributions in legal service cooperation agreement, introducing Hong Kong, information and network of legal service. </seg>
