</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency in Hefei on January 17th (Reporter Wu Yongquan) A few days ago Huangshan Municipal Intermediate People's Court is trailing a gang of robbers and murderers headed by Zhang Haishui, thus putting an end to the criminal acts of the gang headed by Zhang Haishui that have committed rob and murder in over 10 cities of 3 provinces. The case has been supervised by Ministry of Public Security. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> According to the police of Huangshan City, the Zhang Haishui gang consists of 7 members including two mistresses of Zhang Haishui. All its members are from Jiangxi Province. </seg>
<seg id=4> Starting from 1993 the gang fled hither and thither in Huangshan and Anqing cities of Anhui Province, Fuzhou and Jingdezhen cities of Jiangxi Province and Zhejiang Province. In 10 years it committed 7 murder cases, killing 6 innocents 2 of whose bodies were broken into pieces by Zhang's mistresses. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> On June 11th, 2002, Zhang and his gang killed Mr. Hu, a clerk on duty in a franchised tobacco store in Tunxi District of Huangshan City, robbing 30,000 RMB worth of cigarettes. On January 12th, 2003, they killed a person on duty in a store of refrigerator fittings in the same city, robbing several ten thousand yuan worth of enamel-insulated wires. </seg>
<seg id=6> The 2 murder cases arrested the attention of Huangshan Municipal Public Security Bureau and later were included into the cases supervised by Ministry of Public Security. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> The Huangshan police uthorities arrested Zhang Haishui, the prime culprit, and his mistresses on January 18, 2003 in Jingdezhen City. Soon after, such criminals as Cao Runxiang, Zhang Guaxin, Chen Quanwen, Wu Changlian, etc. were apprehended. </seg>
<seg id=8> Zhang Haishui had been in prison for 23 years and other criminals are his relatives or cellmates, and mistresses. </seg>
</p>
