<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency in Tokyo on January 26th (Reporter Le Shaoyan) According to the statistics released by Ministry of Finance in Japan, Japan's import and export set a historical record in 2003. Its trade surplus exceeded 10,000 billion Japanese Yen once again after 3 years. </seg>
