</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> Health officials targeted the aforementioned seafood restaurant for the surprise inspection because a 20-year-old waitress working at this 24-hour restaurant located in the center of Guangzhou's old town areas was officially diagnosed as a suspected SARS case on Wednesday night. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=8> WHO expert Breiman said: "We examined the restaurant very carefully for any potential environmental problems and we will conduct further investigations." </seg>
</p>
