<seg id=7> It is really a miracle that this plane did not crash into the houses or the hospital. </seg>
<seg id=8> At the time, there was a strong wind and the oil was leaking.  If the plane had crashed into the houses or the hospital, </seg>
<seg id=9> it would have certainly caused a huge fire." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> An aviation official at the Transport Ministry said the plane took off this morning from Chofu Airport in western Tokyo and was scheduled to return in two hours. </seg>
