<p>
<seg id=1> West Kowloon Cultural District is a large-scale cultural and arts project Hong Kong has never undertaken before.  It is not only a project that provides our residents with a space for cultural and art pursuits, recreation and entertainment, but also a project to raise the qualities of the urban life and its residents. </seg>
<seg id=2> The construction of West Kowloon Cultural District entails the participation of the entire Hong Kong community. </seg>
