<p>
<seg id=1> China appreciates the efforts of the Counter-Terrorism Committee to promote the implementation of the resolution 1373(2001) in all states and to help enhance the anti-terrorist capabilities of developing countries.  It supports the CTC for strengthening its coordination and cooperation with the relevant international, regional and sub-regional organizations in the global war on terror. </seg>
