<seg id=2> Development is the basis for the progress of human civilization and the key to solving various conflicts and problems the world faces. </seg>
<seg id=3> Only by ensuring a coordinated, balanced and universal development of the world can we achieve long-lasting global peace and stability. </seg>
<seg id=4> We should conduct a comprehensive and in-depth discussion of this issue and make concerted efforts to find its solution. </seg>
