<seg id=7> Catlin also said that the U.S. aid team is free to move around in Bam and no Iranian police are protecting or keeping track of them. </seg>
<seg id=8> He also considered the Iranian government's response to the earthquake and capability to handle the disaster "first-rate and outstanding." </seg>
