<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, January 15 (Reporter Xi Qixin)  The Ministry of Personnel, the Commission of Science, Technology and Industry for National Defense, and the General Armaments Department of the Chinese People's Liberation Army decided the other day to honor advanced units and individuals that made outstanding contributions to China's manned space project. </seg>
