<seg id=5> Moreover, as the young generation in the United States has become more and more liberal toward the homosexuality issue, this act of Bush, though effective in the short term, will do damages to the long-term interest of the Republican Party. </seg>
<seg id=6> Bush's new offensive of "constitutional amendment" can be described as his "scotched earth strategy" for this year's presidential election. </seg>
</p>
